    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "Bloodstone Charm"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "",
        "json": [
          {
            "text": "Supposedly this charm will ward off spells cast by witches, yet all the witches I have met only "
          },
          {
            "text": "ever throw potions at me.  I am not entirely convinced if this thing is useful!"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "manaweaving_altar",
        "location": "mnaw:antisympathy_charm"
      }
    ]
  },
  "Factionless Mages": {
    "index": 11,
    "category": "basics",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "Factionless Mages"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "",
        "json": [
          {
            "text": "Some mages choose to remain factionless, preferring to live in the wilds and avoid the politics "
          },
          {
            "text": "of the faction war.  They are often seen as outcasts, but they are also free to practice their "
          },
          {
            "text": "magic as they see fit."
          },
          {
            "text": "\n\n"
          },
          {
            "text": "Factionless mages are often seen as dangerous, as they are not bound by the laws of the factions. "
          },
          {
            "text": "They have learned some form of sympathetic magic which allows them to cast spells over great "
          },
          {
            "text": "distances, but supposedly their magic is severely curtailed, yet I'm not sure how."
          },
          {
            "text": "\n\n"
          },
          {
            "text": "I have heard that these mages prefer to be referred to as "
          },
          {
            "text": "Hedge Witches",
            "color": "purple"
          },
          {
            "text": ".  This makes me wonder whether they have learned some of their secrets from the wild witches I "
          },
          {
            "text": "have encountered in the swamps.  Perhaps if I can observe a witch in secret I will learn more."
          },
          {
            "text": "\n\n"
          },
          {
            "text": "There are also rumors that some of these factionless mages have forsworn their neutrality and "
          },
          {
            "text": "angered all of the factions.  Woe to these "
          },
          {
            "text": "Spite Witches",
            "color": "red"
          },
          {
              "text": ", for they are hunted by all."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "Dedication": {
